  <entry>
    <title>输入输出流</title>
    <link href="http://na-wen.github.io/2022/05/14/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%81/"/>
    <id>http://na-wen.github.io/2022/05/14/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%81/</id>
    <published>2022-05-14T09:49:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-14T09:51:54.931Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>   <strong>基本概念+标准输入输出流+格式控制+文件操作</strong></p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><p>流 数据单元序列</p><p>读写操作：从文件读到缓冲区，从缓冲区写到文件中</p><p><img src="C:\Users\Dang_Yufan\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220512082715437.png" alt="image-20220512082715437"></p><h2 id="标准输入输出流"><a href="#标准输入输出流" class="headerlink" title="标准输入输出流"></a>标准输入输出流</h2><p>istream的实例对象：std::cin</p><p>输入操作通过&gt;&gt;（重载过的运算符）实现</p><p>&#x2F;&#x2F;读取字符串时会忽略空白符（space，\t,\n,\r,\f,\v）</p><p>判断流状态的函数</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">basic_ios::good</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//true  false输入是不是合法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">basic_ios::eof</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//是否越过流的末尾，注意是越过  ；true,false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (cin.<span class="built_in">eof</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;输入结束。&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*在Windows系列操作系统下，按下组合键Ctrl+z表明数据输入结束；</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">在Unix和Linux包括MAC OS系列操作系统下，按下组合键Ctrl+d表明数据输入结束*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">basic_ios::clear</span><span class="params">( )</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//重置流状态为合法状态</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">basic_istream&amp; <span class="title">basic_istream::ignore</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> count = <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="type">int</span> delim = traits_type::eof())</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//跳过部分字节 注意要再流为合法的状态下使用</span></span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;请输入一个整数:&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    cin.<span class="built_in">ignore</span>(<span class="number">3</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; a;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//输入为12345，输出为45</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">basic_istream&lt;Elem, Tr&gt;&amp; <span class="title">basic_istream::getline</span><span class="params">(Elem *s, <span class="type">int</span> n)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//读取一行数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> s[<span class="number">100</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    cin.<span class="built_in">getline</span>(s, <span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//读取到1234</span></span><br><span class="line">cin.<span class="built_in">get</span>()<span class="comment">//只读一个</span></span><br><span class="line">cin.<span class="built_in">read</span>()<span class="comment">//读取</span></span><br><span class="line">     cin.<span class="built_in">read</span>(s, <span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> s[<span class="number">5</span>] = <span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">// 不能删除这行，read不在s最后补0</span></span><br><span class="line">cin.<span class="built_in">peek</span>()<span class="comment">//返回流要读取的下一个字符</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">put</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>);<span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> s[<span class="number">100</span>] = &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;d&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">write</span>(s,<span class="number">2</span>);<span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">flush</span>();<span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出重定向：命令行：在命令行状态下运行</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;cout&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">    cerr &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;cerr&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">    clog &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;clog&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*命令行状态下，运行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">D:\Examples\CP_Test\Debug&gt;CP_Test   1&gt;out.txt   2&gt;err.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">文件“out.txt”内容变为: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">cout</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">文件“err.txt”内容变为:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">cerr</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">clog*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">ofstream <span class="title">logFile</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">&quot;log.txt&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">clog.<span class="built_in">rdbuf</span>(logFile.<span class="built_in">rdbuf</span>());</span><br><span class="line">clog &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;第一条日志。&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">clog &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;第二条日志。&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*在命令行状态下，运行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">D:\Examples\CP_Test\Debug&gt;CP_Test</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">请按任意键继续. . .</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">文件“log.txt”内容变为: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">第一条日志。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">第二条日志。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="格式控制"><a href="#格式控制" class="headerlink" title="格式控制"></a>格式控制</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;dec&lt;&lt;<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;hex&lt;&lt;<span class="number">10</span>;<span class="comment">//16</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;oct&lt;&lt;<span class="number">10</span>;<span class="comment">//8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//整数的不同进制</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;fixed;<span class="comment">//小数</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;scientific;<span class="comment">//科学计数法</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;hexfloat;<span class="comment">//16</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;defaultfloat;<span class="comment">//系统默认的方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//浮点数的不同格式</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">width</span>(<span class="number">6</span>);<span class="comment">//设置输出的宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">fill</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;12&quot;</span>; <span class="comment">// 输出: xxxx12</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;left;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;right;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;internal;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//对于负数，则在负号与绝对值之间填充字符；</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//否则输出方式同right对应的设置。</span></span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">width</span>(<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">fill</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; internal;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;in&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl; <span class="comment">// 输出xxxin↙</span></span><br><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">width</span>(<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="number">-10</span> &lt;&lt; endl; <span class="comment">// 输出-xx10↙</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//左右对齐</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//精度：在默认的输出形式等格式中，指的是有效数字的个数。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在小数输出形式等格式上，指的是小数点后数字的个数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">streamsize <span class="title">ios_base::precision</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//返回: 当前精度。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">streamsize <span class="title">ios_base::precision</span><span class="params">(streamsize p)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//将输出精度设置为p。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//返回: 在调用本函数之前的精度。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文件输入输出流"><a href="#文件输入输出流" class="headerlink" title="文件输入输出流"></a>文件输入输出流</h2><p>文件流：存储在硬盘等媒介中的数据流被称为文件流；输入叫读，输出叫写 ；</p><p>ifstream  ofstream  </p><fstream><h3 id="文件流操作的基本步骤"><a href="#文件流操作的基本步骤" class="headerlink" title="文件流操作的基本步骤"></a>文件流操作的基本步骤</h3><p>创建文件流的实例对象并打开文件</p><p>读写操作</p><p>关闭文件</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;fstream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">ifstream  <span class="title">fileObject</span> <span class="params">(<span class="string">&quot;in.txt&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//创建并打开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//open(&quot;filename&quot;,openmode)中openmode为整数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (fileObject.<span class="built_in">fail</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;文件&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; filename &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;打开失败。\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//异常检测 若为真则打开失败</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> c;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        c = fileObject.<span class="built_in">get</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//读取</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (fileObject.<span class="built_in">good</span>())<span class="comment">//判断读取的情况</span></span><br><span class="line">            cout.<span class="built_in">put</span>(c);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">while</span> (!fileObject.<span class="built_in">eof</span>());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fileObject&gt;&gt;a;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//读取</span></span><br><span class="line">fileObject&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//写入</span></span><br><span class="line">fileObject.<span class="built_in">close</span>();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;   &lt;strong&gt;基本概念+标准输入输出流+格式控制+文件操作&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
